     doi.org/10.1016/j.chemphys.2008.10.036
  3. Helmich-Paris,B.; de Souza,B.; Neese,F.; Izsák,R.
     An improved chain of spheres for exchange algorithm
     J. Chem. Phys., 2021 155 104109
     doi.org/doi: 10.1063/5.0058766.
